<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2559370>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. – 50% majority-rule consensus phylogram derived from Bayesian inference of combined seven plastid DNA regions. Bayesian posterior probabilities (PP) indicated on the right; maximum likelihood bootstrap (BS) percentages in the middle; parsimony symmetric resampling (SR) percentages on the left [** denotes BS/SR <50%]. DEN. = Dendrokingstonieae; MAL. = Malmeeae; MIL. = Miliuseae; MON. = Monocarpieae; PIP. = Piptostigmateae. Scale bar unit = substitutions per site." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2559370/files/figure.svg" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

